---
// src/pages/02-mobile-menu.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro' // Sesuaikan path layout lo

// Simpan kodingan produksi universal ke string agar aman dari compiler & siap disalin
const codeSnippet = `<!-- Komponen Mobile Menu Navigation Universal -->
<div x-data="{ isOpen: false }" class="relative">

  <!-- Navbar Utama -->
  <header class="bg-slate-900 border-b border-slate-800 px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
    <div class="text-white font-bold">BrandLogo</div>

    <!-- Hamburger Button Super Presisi & Simetris -->
    <button
      @click="isOpen = !isOpen"
      class="relative z-50 w-6 h-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-white focus:outline-none md:hidden"
      aria-label="Toggle Menu"
    >
      <!-- Garis Atas -->
      <span
        :class="isOpen ? 'rotate-45 absolute' : '-translate-y-1.5'"
        class="w-5 h-0.5 bg-current transform transition duration-300 ease-in-out"
      ></span>

      <!-- Garis Tengah -->
      <span
        :class="isOpen ? 'opacity-0 scale-0' : 'opacity-100'"
        class="w-5 h-0.5 bg-current transition duration-300 ease-in-out"
      ></span>

      <!-- Garis Bawah -->
      <span
        :class="isOpen ? '-rotate-45 absolute' : 'translate-y-1.5'"
        class="w-5 h-0.5 bg-current transform transition duration-300 ease-in-out"
      ></span>
    </button>
  </header>

  <!-- Overlay Full-Screen Menu Mobile -->
  <div
    x-show="isOpen"
    x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-300"
    x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 -translate-y-4"
    x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0"
    x-transition:leave="transition ease-in duration-200"
    x-transition:leave-start="opacity-100 translate-y-0"
    x-transition:leave-end="opacity-0 -translate-y-4"
    class="fixed inset-0 z-40 bg-slate-950/95 backdrop-blur-lg flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-8 md:hidden"
    x-cloak
  >
    <nav class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-300">
      <a href="#" @click="isOpen = false" class="hover:text-sky-400 transition-colors">Dashboard</a>
      <a href="#" @click="isOpen = false" class="hover:text-sky-400 transition-colors">Services</a>
      <a href="#" @click="isOpen = false" class="hover:text-sky-400 transition-colors">Portfolios</a>
      <a href="#" @click="isOpen = false" class="hover:text-sky-400 transition-colors">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</div>`
---

<Layout title="02. Mobile Menu Overlay - Blueprint UI">
  <main
    class="bg-slate-955 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12 font-sans text-slate-100"
  >
    <!-- HEADER: Judul & Deskripsi Fitur -->
    <header class="mb-8 border-b border-slate-800 pb-6">
      <div class="mb-2 flex items-center gap-3">
        <span
          class="rounded-md border border-sky-500/30 bg-sky-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] font-bold text-sky-400"
          >02. MUDAH</span
        >
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
          Mobile Menu Overlay
        </h1>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
        Navigasi menu mobile dengan animasi transformasi hamburger (garis tiga
        menjadi icon X) disertai panel menu overlay modern ber-efek blur
        transparan yang universal untuk segala jenis website.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- SECTION 1: Live Preview Playground -->
    <section class="mb-12" aria-labelledby="preview-title">
      <h2
        id="preview-title"
        class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-400 uppercase"
      >
        Live Preview
      </h2>

      <!-- Container Utama Simulasi Layar HP (Terisolasi menggunakan absolute agar overlay tidak bocor keluar container) -->
      <div
        class="relative mx-auto h-100 w-full max-w-sm overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 shadow-2xl"
      >
        <!-- Pintu Masuk Komponen Playground -->
        <div
          x-data="{ isOpen: false }"
          class="relative flex h-full w-full flex-col"
        >
          <!-- Simulasi Nav Header -->
          <header
            class="relative z-50 flex items-center justify-between border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 px-5 py-4"
          >
            <div class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider text-white">
              CORE<span class="text-sky-400">LAB</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Hamburger Button Interaktif -->
            <button
              @click="isOpen = !isOpen"
              class="flex h-4 w-5 flex-col items-center justify-between text-slate-300 hover:text-white focus:outline-none"
              aria-label="Toggle Menu"
            >
              <span
                :class="isOpen ? 'rotate-45 translate-y-1.75' : ''"
                class="h-0.5 w-full transform bg-current transition duration-300 ease-in-out"
              ></span>
              <span
                :class="isOpen ? 'opacity-0' : ''"
                class="h-0.5 w-full bg-current transition duration-300 ease-in-out"
              ></span>
              <span
                :class="isOpen ? '-rotate-45 -translate-y-1.75' : ''"
                class="h-0.5 w-full transform bg-current transition duration-300 ease-in-out"
              ></span>
            </button>
          </header>

          <!-- Simulasi Isi Halaman Pasif Belakang Menu -->
          <div
            class="flex flex-1 flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center opacity-20"
          >
            <div class="mb-2 h-12 w-12 rounded-full bg-slate-800"></div>
            <div class="mb-1 h-3 w-24 rounded bg-slate-800"></div>
            <div class="h-2 w-32 rounded bg-slate-800"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- INTERNAL PREVIEW OVERLAY: Dikurung pake absolute (Khusus simulasi agar gak menutupi 1 screen monitor lo) -->
          <div
            x-show="isOpen"
            x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-300"
            x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 -translate-y-4"
            x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0"
            x-transition:leave="transition ease-in duration-200"
            x-transition:leave-start="opacity-100 translate-y-0"
            x-transition:leave-end="opacity-0 -translate-y-4"
            class="absolute inset-0 z-40 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 bg-slate-900/95 backdrop-blur-md"
            x-cloak
          >
            <nav
              class="flex flex-col items-center gap-5 text-sm font-medium text-slate-300"
            >
              <span
                @click="isOpen = false"
                class="cursor-pointer transition-colors hover:text-sky-400"
                >Dashboard</span
              >
              <span
                @click="isOpen = false"
                class="cursor-pointer transition-colors hover:text-sky-400"
                >Services</span
              >
              <span
                @click="isOpen = false"
                class="cursor-pointer transition-colors hover:text-sky-400"
                >Portfolios</span
              >
              <span
                @click="isOpen = false"
                class="cursor-pointer transition-colors hover:text-sky-400"
                >Contact Us</span
              >
            </nav>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 2: Code Snippet Block (Siap Salin) -->
    <section class="mb-12" aria-labelledby="code-title">
      <h2
        id="code-title"
        class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-400 uppercase"
      >
        Clean Code (Production Ready)
      </h2>
      <article x-data="codeCopier" class="group relative">
        <!-- Tombol Salin Cepat Berbasis Font Awesome Referensi Sebelumnya -->
        <button
          @click="copy()"
          :class="copied ? 'bg-emerald-500/20 border-emerald-500/40 text-emerald-400' : 'bg-slate-950/60 border-slate-800 text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-900'"
          class="absolute top-3 right-3 z-10 flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-200 active:scale-95"
          aria-label="Salin kode"
        >
          <i x-show="!copied" class="fa-regular fa-copy text-sm"></i>
          <i
            x-show="copied"
            class="fa-solid fa-check text-sm text-emerald-400"
            x-cloak></i>
          <span x-text="copied ? 'Copied!' : 'Copy'"></span>
        </button>

        <!-- Block Pre Code -->
        <pre
          class="h-100 overflow-auto rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5 pr-20 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-300"><code>{codeSnippet}</code></pre>
      </article>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 3: Dokumentasi & Catatan Teknis -->
    <section aria-labelledby="doc-title">
      <h2
        id="doc-title"
        class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-400 uppercase"
      >
        Dokumentasi Logika
      </h2>
      <article
        class="space-y-4 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800/60 bg-slate-900/50 p-5 text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-400 md:text-sm"
      >
        <p>
          <strong class="text-slate-200"
            >1. Transformasi Baris Hamburger:</strong
          > Manipulasi animasi tombol menggunakan class `:class="isOpen ? 'rotate-45
          translate-y-[Xpx]' : ''"`. Garis tengah dihilangkan lewat opacity, sementara
          garis atas dan bawah diputar silang 45 derajat secara otomatis.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-slate-200"
            >2. Manajemen Transisi Direktivitas:</strong
          > Fitur <code class="font-mono text-yellow-400">x-transition</code> mempermudah
          efek masuk panel menu. Kita set titik mula koordinat sumbu Y sedikit keatas
          (<code class="font-mono text-slate-300">-translate-y-4</code>) dengan
          opasitas nol agar menu terasa turun mengalir halus dari atas saat
          dibuka.
        </p>
        <blockquote
          class="rounded-r-md border-l-2 border-sky-500 bg-sky-500/5 px-4 py-2 text-slate-300"
        >
          <strong>Tip Integrasi:</strong> Pada kode Clean Code di atas, panel menu
          menggunakan posisi <code class="font-mono text-sky-400"
            >fixed inset-0</code
          > agar memakan space layar penuh browser proyeksian asli lo. Jaga tumpukan
          lapisan indeks menggunakan kelas z-index tinggi (<code
            class="font-mono text-sky-400">z-40</code
          > keatas).
        </blockquote>
      </article>
    </section>

    <!-- Tombol Kembali -->
    <footer class="mt-12 border-t border-slate-900 pt-6">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-500 transition-colors hover:text-white"
      >
        ← Kembali ke Dashboard Sandbox
      </a>
    </footer>
  </main>
</Layout>

<!-- Script Logic Handler Salin Anti-bug compiler Astro -->
<script define:vars={{ codeSnippet }}>
  document.addEventListener('alpine:init', () => {
    Alpine.data('codeCopier', () => ({
      copied: false,
      codeText: codeSnippet,

      copy() {
        navigator.clipboard.writeText(this.codeText)
        this.copied = true
        setTimeout(() => {
          this.copied = false
        }, 2000)
      },
    }))
  })
</script>
